<h1 style="font-size:20px; line-height:22px; height:22px; margin-bottom:10px;">蜉蝣</h1>
<p class="source"><a href="https://www.gushiwen.org/shiwen/default.aspx?cstr=%e5%85%88%e7%a7%a6">先秦</a><span>：</span><a href="/search.aspx?value=%e4%bd%9a%e5%90%8d">佚名</a> </p>
<div class="contson" id="contson8309cf56c239">
<p>蜉蝣之羽，衣裳楚楚。心之忧矣，於我归处。<br />蜉蝣之翼，采采衣服。心之忧矣，於我归息。<br />蜉蝣掘阅，麻衣如雪。心之忧矣，於我归说。<br /></p>
</div>
</div>
